nodes.text: The Toorna's Profits was a freighter that landed on Vogga the Hutt's dock on Nar Shaddaa. The landing was delayed however, due to a mix-up of the ID signatures of the Toorna's Profits, the Silver Zephyr, and the Alakandor.
